6/12/01
  Noticed that picture jump problem is visible with local time base.
  I have not seen such problem with input time base.

  Modify output watchdog to support input time base mode


6/13/01
  Verified that input timebase mode works with GI DCT 1000 decoder.
  That is, if the source has no problem, DPI will not create the problem.
  If the source already has the problem, DPI will not make it worse, neither
  will it try to solve the problem.
